'''dicotyledon'''
# any plant in what used to be the ''[[Dicotyledones]]'' (also written ''Dicotyledonae'') or ''[[Magnoliopsida]]'', a class in the ''Angiospermae'', the [[flowering plant]]s. Dicotyledons are [[bean]]s, [[buttercup]]s, [[oak]]s, [[sunflower]]s, etc.
